{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "阿尔贝琉斯将蕴含着抑制魔兽之力的\\n“圣片”放置于王国各地。\\n传说中，“圣片”是由阿尔贝琉斯\\n击碎伊莉雅教会所保管的一件武器而来。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "龙的巢穴就快到了。\\n噢，对了，\\n尤蒂尔，塞西娅。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_01_04_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "你们寻求的“圣片”，\\n到底是什么东西？\\n可以说得再详细点吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_01_04_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "你说“圣片”啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_01_04_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "圣片是一种碎片，\\n其中蕴含着抑制魔兽出现的力量。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_01_04_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "它们被放置在王国各地，\\n充当护符。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_01_04_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "减少魔兽的护符……\\n也就是说，是那种吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_01_04_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "只要带着它，\\n就可以轻松穿越满是魔兽的地方。\\n那真是不错啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_01_04_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "不、不是这样的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_01_04_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "只有与龙缔结契约的人\\n才能挪动圣片。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_01_04_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "啊？\\n为什么？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_01_04_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "因为如果能被随意挪动，会很麻烦。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_01_04_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "圣片通常被放置在\\n王国中尤为不洁之处。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_01_04_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "供奉圣片的人\\n为了圣片不被轻易挪动，\\n就定下了这样的规矩。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_01_04_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "那个供奉圣片的家伙是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_01_04_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "就是最早与龙缔结契约的王族。\\n也就是我们的祖先——\\n建国之王阿尔贝琉斯。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_01_04_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "建国之王阿尔贝琉斯！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_01_04_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "我一直以为这是说给小鬼听的童话，\\n没想到是真的啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_01_04_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "没错，国王叹惋荒芜的世界，\\n于是把伊莉雅教会中的“某件物品”击碎，\\n作为圣片。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_01_04_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "然后将它们放置于各处，\\n并规定只有能与龙缔结契约之人，\\n也就是自己的子孙才可挪动。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_01_04_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "原来如此。\\n听起来是个了不起的人啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_01_04_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "谢了，我大概明白圣片是什么了。\\n不过，还有最后一个问题。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_01_04_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "你说阿尔贝琉斯击碎了“某件物品”，\\n这个“某件物品”\\n到底是什么？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_01_04_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "是水晶球吗，还是什么瓶子？\\n总觉得很在意……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_01_04_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "圣片的原物吗。\\n我不是很清楚，\\n不过应该是教会代代相传的古老圣遗物。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_01_04_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "塞西娅，你知道些什么吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_01_04_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "嗯。圣片的原物……\\n听说是与女神伊莉雅有因缘的\\n一件强大的武器。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_01_04_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "只要挥动它，\\n就足以瞬间平息整片大陆……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_01_04_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "武器吗。\\n那为什么阿尔贝琉斯\\n不自己使用呢？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_01_04_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "要是我的话，\\n就尽情挥动，\\n自己消灭魔兽了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_01_04_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "如果能永远活着，\\n或许他就这么做了吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_01_04_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "但是，人无法永生。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_01_04_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "嗯，也是。\\n死了就全没了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_01_04_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "没错。\\n阿尔贝琉斯王是为了后世考虑。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_01_04_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "为了在自己死后，\\n王国的民众也能够受到庇佑……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_01_04_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "寄托着建国之王心愿的圣片……\\n时至今日，\\n也时刻庇佑着我们。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_01_04_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}